<h1>Sticker Haven</h1>
<section>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Sticker Haven is a printing company founded with the goal of providing cheap, fast, and high quality sticker printing options for artists and small businesses!</p>
    <p>This venture was inspired by the art and sticker culture at Worcester Polytechnic Institute. Many people wanted to make custom stickers, but buying online and having to pay tons for shipping or being required to order large quantities was difficult. For many, the solution was to purchase a desktop vinyl cutter, but I have heard complaints about them being tedius to work with. To fill this gap, I purchased a professional grade printer and cutter to provide an option for students interested in ordering quantities of around 50-200 stickers without breaking the bank or having to struggle with a small vinyl cutter.</p>
</section>